WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.920
E-learning

00:00:00.920 --> 00:00:04.800
one of the most effective ways to communicate
a lot of important information

00:00:04.800 --> 00:00:09.240
within your company, towards customers,
or even to other professionals.

00:00:09.680 --> 00:00:13.760
Research shows that e-learning can be
just as effective or even better than

00:00:13.760 --> 00:00:16.000
physical courses and classroom education

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:18.840
without the problems that arise
with physical gathering

00:00:18.840 --> 00:00:21.680
such as travel costs, absence,

00:00:21.680 --> 00:00:25.880
and not being able to rewind when
your concentration lapses for a minute.

00:00:26.720 --> 00:00:28.280
My name is Django van den Busken.

00:00:28.680 --> 00:00:31.600
I'm a specialist in using video
as a communication tool

00:00:31.760 --> 00:00:35.800
and I want to help you write, record
and publish your e-learning.

00:00:36.360 --> 00:00:40.640
My goal is to make this orderly,
simple and effective

00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:43.480
to save you from headaches
as much as possible.

00:00:44.400 --> 00:00:48.000
You can request a free meeting
down below for more information

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:50.080
or send an email via the contact form.

00:00:50.440 --> 00:00:54.040
Want to know more about our crash course
for improving presentation skills?

00:00:54.200 --> 00:00:57.120
Go to 24film.nl/coaching.

00:00:57.560 --> 00:00:58.320
Until next time.

